DAT
id=qid::label=str::text=lstr::
26785::$$$message_0229_0000_0000$$$::And then night falls.[lr]::
26786::$$$message_0229_0000_0001$$$::I did not talk to Saber or Tohsaka in the other room, and nothing much happened until it was bedtime.::
26787::$$$message_0229_0001_0000$$$::It's eleven now.[lr]::
26788::$$$message_0229_0001_0001$$$::The lights in the house are off, and everyone inside goes to sleep to prepare for the upcoming day.::
26789::$$$message_0229_0002_0000$$$::...[lr]::
26790::$$$message_0229_0002_0001$$$::...[lr]::
26791::$$$message_0229_0002_0002$$$::...[lr]::
26792::$$$message_0229_0002_0003$$$::"...I can't sleep."::
26793::$$$message_0229_0003_0000$$$::I'm still lying on my side, eyes wide open.[lr]::
26794::$$$message_0229_0003_0001$$$::This is my room. I should be sleeping. But it feels completely different now.::
26795::$$$message_0229_0004_0000$$$::"Damn. Why can't I..."[lr]::
26796::$$$message_0229_0004_0001$$$::It's quiet, but I hear Saber's breathing in the next room.[lr]::
26797::$$$message_0229_0004_0002$$$::Argh, I know. Of course I can hear sound coming from the next room if it's quiet! And since I can hear her breathing, I find myself imagining Saber's sleeping form. ::
26798::$$$message_0229_0005_0000$$$::"Argh, dammit! How the hell can I fall asleep in this situation!?"[lr]::
26799::$$$message_0229_0005_0001$$$::I can't just stay in this whole bed of needles situation forever![lr]::
26800::$$$message_0229_0005_0002$$$::I sneak out of my futon, trying not to wake Saber up.::
26801::$$$message_0229_0006_0000$$$::"Thank goodness. I thought Saber would notice, but I guess not."[lr]::
26802::$$$message_0229_0006_0001$$$::Unless she's a deep sleeper.[lr]::
26803::$$$message_0229_0006_0002$$$::I question whether she can really protect her Master this way, but there's no immediate danger.[lr]::
26804::$$$message_0229_0006_0003$$$::If Servants are linked to Masters, she would probably wake up immediately if her Master is in danger.::
26805::$$$message_0229_0007_0000$$$::"Tohsaka...seems to be asleep."[lr]::
26806::$$$message_0229_0007_0001$$$::The lights in the detached building are out.[lr]::
26807::$$$message_0229_0007_0002$$$::She's either just that defiant, or maybe she's naturally adaptable...[lr]::
26808::$$$message_0229_0007_0003$$$::Because Tohsaka managed to blend in here in just a day.::
26809::$$$message_0229_0008_0000$$$::"Well honestly, it does help having her around."[lr]::
26810::$$$message_0229_0008_0001$$$::Yep. She's a handful, but she is helpful.[lr]::
26811::$$$message_0229_0008_0002$$$::One bit of evidence of that is the bandage wrapped around my hand.::
26812::$$$message_0229_0009_0000$$$::"Hide my Command Spells, huh? I never would have thought to do that if it hadn't been pointed out."[lr]::
26813::$$$message_0229_0009_0001$$$::The Command Spells Masters bear appear somewhere on their arm.[lr]::
26814::$$$message_0229_0009_0002$$$::Mine appeared on the back of my left hand.[lr]::
26815::$$$message_0229_0009_0003$$$::Clothes won't work to hide it, so I'll need to use bandages, even if it looks a bit awkward.::
26816::$$$message_0229_0010_0000$$$::"It's wintertime, so I'll wear some long sleeves to hide it."[lr]::
26817::$$$message_0229_0010_0001$$$::Tohsaka has hers on the opposite hand from mine, around the middle of her right hand or somewhere around there. [lr]::
26818::$$$message_0229_0010_0002$$$::The shape of Command Spells differ for each Master, and I don't think I'll ever see Tohsaka's Command Spell.::
26819::$$$message_0229_0011_0000$$$::Silence falls over the shed.[lr]::
26820::$$$message_0229_0011_0001$$$::This is where Lancer cornered me yesterday...[lr]::
26821::$$$message_0229_0011_0002$$$::...and where Saber appeared.[lr]::
26822::$$$message_0229_0011_0003$$$::The entrance is still open, and it's pitch dark inside, as if to repel anyone who might try to enter.::
26823::$$$message_0229_0012_0000$$$::But this darkness is familiar to me.[lr]::
26824::$$$message_0229_0012_0001$$$::I used to play here when I was young, and I feel it to be my real room. It sits silently under the wintry night sky.::
26825::$$$message_0229_0013_0000$$$::I step inside.[lr]::
26826::$$$message_0229_0013_0001$$$::After closing the door to shut out the cold, I turn on the stove.::
26827::$$$message_0229_0014_0000$$$::"I thought I would take a break today, but I shouldn't. The old man would be rolling in his grave if he knew I skipped my training two days in a row."[lr]::
26828::$$$message_0229_0014_0001$$$::I sit down in the middle of the shed and take a deep breath.[lr]::
26829::$$$message_0229_0014_0002$$$::I should train. No pauses.[lr]::
26830::$$$message_0229_0014_0003$$$::Magecraft is a mental discipline to me, so I shouldn't skimp on my training for no good reason.::
26831::$$$message_0229_0015_0000$$$::"Breath...in."[lr]::
26832::$$$message_0229_0015_0001$$$::I begin my training by getting my breathing under control.[lr]::
26833::$$$message_0229_0015_0002$$$::The usual images pop into my head.[lr]::
26834::$$$message_0229_0015_0003$$$::The image of a sword drifts into my empty mind.::
26835::$$$message_0229_0016_0000$$$::[font italic=true]...[font italic=false][lr]::
26836::$$$message_0229_0016_0001$$$::I try to ignore it and clear my head.[lr]::
26837::$$$message_0229_0016_0002$$$::As soon as magical energy run through my body, I begin my usual training.::
26838::$$$message_0229_0017_0000$$$::My Strengthening magecraft succeeded for the first time in years when I was attacked by Lancer last night.[lr]::
26839::$$$message_0229_0017_0001$$$::I need to recreate that same feeling before I forget, or else it'll have been for nothing.[lr]::
26840::$$$message_0229_0017_0002$$$::"Trace...on."[lr]::
26841::$$$message_0229_0017_0003$$$::I close my eyes halfway and release the air from my lungs.::
26842::$$$message_0229_0018_0000$$$::That's all can do for now.[lr]::
26843::$$$message_0229_0018_0001$$$::As I concentrate, everything fades away[line2]the Holy Grail War, Saber, Tohsaka.[lr]::
26844::$$$message_0229_0018_0002$$$::If I allow my thoughts to slide into nothingness, any immature hesitations will fall away, and I'll finally get a good night's sleep.::

